<p>3項間漸化式 <span style="font-style:italic;">G</span><span style="font-size:60%;vertical-align:sub;"><span style="font-style:italic;">k</span></span> = <span style="font-style:italic;">G</span><span style="font-size:60%;vertical-align:sub;"><span style="font-style:italic;">k</span>-1</span> + <span style="font-style:italic;">G</span><span style="font-size:60%;vertical-align:sub;"><span style="font-style:italic;">k</span>-2</span>, <span style="font-style:italic;">G</span><span style="font-size:60%;vertical-align:sub;">1</span> = 1, <span style="font-style:italic;">G</span><span style="font-size:60%;vertical-align:sub;">2</span> = 4 (<span style="font-style:italic;">G</span><span style="font-size:60%;vertical-align:sub;"><span style="font-style:italic;">k</span></span> = 1, 4, 5, 9, 14, 23, ...) によって与えられる無限級数 <span style="font-style:italic;">A</span><span style="font-size:60%;vertical-align:sub;"><span style="font-style:italic;">G</span></span>(<span style="font-style:italic;">x</span>) = <span style="font-style:italic;">xG</span><span style="font-size:60%;vertical-align:sub;">1</span> + <span style="font-style:italic;">x</span><span style="font-size:60%;vertical-align:super;">2</span><span style="font-style:italic;">G</span><span style="font-size:60%;vertical-align:sub;">2</span> + <span style="font-style:italic;">x</span><span style="font-size:60%;vertical-align:super;">3</span><span style="font-style:italic;">G</span><span style="font-size:60%;vertical-align:sub;">3</span> + ... を考える。</p>
<p>この問題では、<span style="font-style:italic;">A</span><span style="font-size:60%;vertical-align:sub;"><span style="font-style:italic;">G</span></span>(<span style="font-style:italic;">x</span>) が正の整数となるような x の値について考える。</p>
<p>最初の5つの自然数に対する x の値を下表に示す。</p>
